'''比亚迪e6'''是一款由[[比亚迪汽车|比亚迪汽车]]生产的[[純電動車|纯电动]][[多功能休旅車|多功能休旅車]]，它的续航里程能够达到{{convert|195|km|0|abbr=on}}或以上<ref name=Bloomberg0310>{{cite web |last1=Tian |first1=Ying |first2=Stanley |last2=James |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=newsarchive&sid=aNMr8oxbgSKo |title=BYD Scales Back Its Electric-Car Plans, Morning Post Reports |publisher=[[Bloomberg.com|Bloomberg.com]] |date=2010-03-16 |accessdate=2010-03-19 |archive-date=2010-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100527102718/http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=newsarchive&sid=aNMr8oxbgSKo |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=EVNews/>。2010年5月，40辆[[比亚迪|比亚迪]]e6[[出租車|出租車]]在[[深圳市|深圳市]]投入运营<ref name=EVNews>{{cite web|url=http://electric-vehicles-cars-bikes.blogspot.com/2010/05/byd-e6-electric-taxis-hit-roads-in.html|title=BYD E6 Taxis Hit Roads in South China City|publisher=Electric Vehicle News|date=2010-05-18|accessdate=2010-05-23|archive-date=2011-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110815141327/http://electric-vehicles-cars-bikes.blogspot.com/2010/05/byd-e6-electric-taxis-hit-roads-in.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。因为充电设备等基础设施的不完善，直到2011年10月26日，比亚迪才开始向普通用户销售这一车型（原定时间为2009年）<ref>{{cite web | title = Keep Dangling the Carrot: BYD Postpones General Release of the All-Electric e6 Yet Again | url = http://chinaautoweb.com/2010/09/byd-postpones-release-of-the-e6-yet-again/ | publisher = ChinaAutoWeb | date = 2010-09-03 | accessdate = 2013-07-31 | archive-date = 2011-11-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111114112426/http://chinaautoweb.com/2010/09/byd-postpones-release-of-the-e6-yet-again/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="BYD e6 public">{{cite news|title=First Pure-Electric Vehicle now available for Consumers in China |url=http://www.bydenergy.com/bydenergy/energy/News%20Center/News/78.html |accessdate=29 October 2011 |newspaper=BYD Energy |date=27 October 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111101200501/http://www.bydenergy.com/bydenergy/energy/News%20Center/News/78.html |archivedate=2011-11-01}}</ref>。在北美，e6车型的发布同样因为基础设施问题经历了屡次延期<ref name=USPrice>{{cite web|url=http://www.plugincars.com/exclusive-byd-executive-provides-breakthrough-us-pricing-chinese-electric-car.html|title=BYD Announces Breakthrough U.S. Pricing for Chinese Long-Range Electric Cars|publisher=PluginCars.com|author=Brad Berman|date=2011-01-09|accessdate=2011-01-11|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212004211/https://www.plugincars.com/exclusive-byd-executive-provides-breakthrough-us-pricing-chinese-electric-car.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Bloomber1011>{{cite news|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-23/buffett-s-chinese-car-investment-fails-to-bring-los-angeles-promised-jobs.html|title=Buffett-Backed Carmaker Arrives in L.A. Late With Fewer Jobs|author=Alan Ohnsman and Christopher Palmeri|date=2011-10-24|accessdate=2011-10-29|archive-date=2017-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170224153455/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-23/buffett-s-chinese-car-investment-fails-to-bring-los-angeles-promised-jobs.html/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年5月，比亚迪宣布在北美只针对车队用户销售e6汽车，转而专注于纯电动公交车[[比亚迪K9|k9]]<ref name=USfleetsonly>{{cite web|url=http://www.greencarreports.com/news/1084033_byd-e6-chinese-electric-car-wont-be-sold-to-consumers-in-u-s|title=BYD e6 Chinese Electric Car Won't Be Sold To Consumers In U.S.|author=Antony Ingram|publisher=Green Car Reports|date=2013-04-08|accessdate=2013-05-11|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126094844/https://www.greencarreports.com/news/1084033_byd-e6-chinese-electric-car-wont-be-sold-to-consumers-in-u-s|dead-url=no}}</ref>。从2010到2013年6月，在中国市场共有2,854辆e6汽车被售出。

